Package lombok.installer Description

This package contains the lombok installer. It explains to any user that double-clicks the lombok.jar what lombok is about, and has the ability to instrument (or remove existing Lombok instrumentation) from any Eclipse installation. This package also contains the graphics uses in the installer in SVG format.
